summary: I made a Mariah Carey 'Inspired' preset I'm sharing cuz I LOVE Mariah Carey.
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=6]﻿[/size][size=6]HI Humans! ^~^

[img]https://i.imgur.com/AVo1QKf.jpg[/img]
[/size][size=6][b]~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~[/b][/size]

[size=4]This is like legit my first ever mod/ basically preset.[/size]

[size=4]Thank you for checking it out, it means a lot to me. :)[/size]


[color=#ff0000][size=6]Introduction
[/size]-------------------------------

[/color][size=4]I was wandering bing.com one day, reading the news like I always do, when all of a sudden I saw a SUPER DUPER saad pic of Mariah Carey, looking all like this:[/size]
[img]https://i.imgur.com/Q4BzoWh.jpg[/img]
[size=4]and I was all like:[/size]
[img]https://i.imgur.com/0JXtlX3.jpg[/img]
[size=4]DEEEHEWHERUURAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAW! Why is she so sad lookin??!?!?![/size]
[size=4]So I made her into a preset.[/size]



[color=#ff0000][size=6]MOD REQUIREMENTS [/size][/color][color=#ff0000][size=1](I guess I mean, like, hey I guess its no big deal and all)
[/size][/color][color=#ff0000]--------------------[/color]


[size=3][b]*KS Hairstyles Renweal
[/b]
[b]*Demoniac- High Quality Gloss (This is a hard requirement if you wwant her looking good)

*Eyes of Aber 

*I use unp tbbp body, you might need xmpse extended and stuff I think

*Racemenu (Hard Requirement)

*An imaginary electric Guitar to rock out on ^~^[/b]


[/size]Let me know if you aquire assistance to get her to work or look like my ingame version, I will assist in what I can.


[size=6][b]~~~~THANK YOU HUMANS!~~~~
